  "commit_message": "docs: set up GitHub web-flow as a committer (#99)\n\n* docs: how to set up GitHub web-flow as a committer\n\nNew workflows page explaining that commits made via the GitHub web UI\n(edit-in-browser, Merge/Squash/Rebase buttons, web reverts) are GPG-\nsigned by GitHub's web-flow key as GitHub <noreply@github.com>, and\nhow to make them verify in ReARM: fetch github.com/web-flow.gpg,\ncreate a \"GitHub\" committer, and enrol the web-flow GPG public key.\nWired into the workflows sidebar + index.\n\nReARM-Agenti",
